libshapedraw.internal.bootstrap

Class FMLModLibShapeDraw

  • java.lang.Object
    • libshapedraw.internal.bootstrap.LSDBootstrapBase
      • libshapedraw.internal.bootstrap.FMLModLibShapeDraw
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MinecraftAccess

    public class FMLModLibShapeDraw
extends LSDBootstrapBase
    Internal class. Mods using the LibShapeDraw API can safely ignore this. Rather, instantiate LibShapeDraw.

    This is a Forge/FML mod (independent, but compatible with LiteLoader) that delegates bootstrapping LibShapeDraw to the wrapper abstraction (see LSDBootstrapBase).
